Graco,25M530,,Graco CM20 ToughTek Continuous Mixer,simple,"<p>For large jobs, the affordable CM20 continuous mixer achieves higher output than traditional methods and comparable mixers while maintaining a high-quality mix. In addition, the CM20 is the first continuous mixer on the market to be rated for a standard 120V circuit so you can plug it in and start mixing anywhere on the site.</p> <p>Automatic mixers for cementitious materials</p> <p>Easy to operate, easy to move</p> <p>Plug and play – CM20 rated for a 120V circuit</p> <p>Variable pump output lets you adjust material flow</p> <p>Flow rate: 18 gpm (70 lpm)</p> <p>Output (underlayment): up to 40 bags per hour (based on 80-lb/36 kg bags)</p> <p>Hopper capacity: 16 Gal (60.6 L)</p> <p>Power requirements: 230V, 30A, 1-ph or 230V, 30A, 3-ph</p> <p>Easy to take apart for quick clean-up and transport</p> <p>Easy to maintain with long-wearing parts and components</p>","For large jobs, the affordable CM20 continuous mixer achieves higher output than traditional methods and comparable mixers while maintaining a high-quality mix. In addition, the CM20 is the first continuous mixer on the market to be rated for a standard 120V circuit so you can plug it in and start mixing anywhere on the site.",10380.00,,https://drywalltoolbox.com/wp/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Graco/Products/25m530.webp,Texture Tools > Graco > Texture Sprayers,Graco,566,1,0,visible,,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,,,,,,,,,Brand,Graco,1,1
