Graco,20B473,,Graco Ultra QuickShot,simple,"<p>The Ultra QuickShot is a breakthrough technology, designed to deliver higher quality and provide results faster, created for the perfect airless finish, while virtually eliminating spits. Built with extreme spray control to quickly adjust pressure for every application.</p> <p>The industry's most portable sprayer allows you to spray in the tightest of areas with precision and the highest control. Spray the broadest range of architectural coatings, from water-based paints, to solvents, and flammable-based materials. Perfect for small jobs such as cabinets, doors, trim, soffits, gutters, and more.</p> <p>Instant Response Electric Powered Gun Virtually Eliminates Spits</p> <p>Reduce fatigue with the industry's lightest trigger pull</p> <p>Smallest, lightest airless gun ever built</p> <p>Responds instantly to produce the best finish</p> <p>On-Demand Precision Flow-Control System</p> <p>Quickly adjust the material flow for extreme airless spray control</p> <p>Easily dial-in to your desired pressure from 100-2,000 psi</p> <p>6 ft Flexible Hose For Full Reach &amp; Easy Hose Management</p> <p>Easily prime, change colors, and clean in seconds</p> <p>The gun and hose hold only 1 oz of coating</p> <p>QuickShot ProConnect Airless Piston Pump</p> <p>Durable long-life triple piston pump</p> <p>32 oz Pour-N-Go Cup</p> <p>Easy fill design - refill on your hip</p> <p>Spray small amounts FAST</p> <p>Power to Take on Every Small Job</p> <p>It comes with two DEWALT 20V Lithium-ion batteries</p> <p>Spray up to one gallon on each battery</p> <p>Ultimate Hands-Free Portability With Belt and Holster Attachment</p>","The Ultra QuickShot is a breakthrough technology, designed to deliver higher quality and provide results faster, created for the perfect airless finish, while virtually eliminating spits.",1399.00,,https://drywalltoolbox.com/wp/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Graco/Products/20b473.webp,Texture Tools > Graco > Texture Sprayers,Graco,618,1,0,visible,,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,,,,,,,,,Brand,Graco,1,1
